{"tid":950622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那國防部認丟失魚雷被越南漁民撈獲","createTime":"2018-12-21T16:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T18:19:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6ad06c1c9513f374c0796b8f2443d868be9ca240","tid":950622,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181221/s00004/1fe88f75bc2308d50397016943e77a87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181221%2Fs00004%2F1fe88f75bc2308d50397016943e77a87.jpg&h=f8b0b09a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越南富安省有漁民，日前於海中發現一枚刻有簡體漢字的魚雷。支那國防部證實，該魚雷是支那海軍丟失，強調僅為一般訓練用雷，沒有任何針對目標。<br />\n<br />\n國防部今早證實，支那海軍本月初在海南島東部附近海域組織海上訓練時，丟失一枚魚雷，其後可能因海流漂向越方近海，強調該魚雷僅為一般訓練用雷，沒有任何針對目標。<br />\n<br />\n海軍專家王雲飛接受內地傳媒訪問時表示，訓練魚雷的彈頭不裝炸藥，供訓練和試驗使用，並能回收，橘紅色標誌就是為了方便撈雷。他又指，一般訓練魚雷有專用的頻段，與戰雷不一樣，「撈走了沒什麼影響，核心機密不會泄露」。<br />\n<br />\n越南漁民Tran Minh Thanh周二（18日）於中部海域捕魚時，於離岸約4海浬發現一枚長6.8米、直徑約54厘米的魚雷，上面刻有簡體漢字。他將魚雷撈上岸後，通報越南當局。"},{"pid":"85e94ac77e80a299afa9ed67fbb91d20662beeac","tid":950622,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35647965762e8a526991ec126e4b0b4a88af2a7c","tid":950622,"uid":11301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:45:17.000Z","msg":"小小支那 可笑可笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e76d75c2d0f1a970f58613a5ff3dff5c01a8afb","tid":950622,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT